## Current Issue Analysis
The sorting problem likely stems from users not understanding **how conversations are sorted** and **when sorting updates happen**. WhatsApp uses a hybrid model: pinned conversations + recency (last message time).

## 1. Sorting Behavior & Visual Indicators

